org.apache.hadoop.hbase.util

类 LoadTestTool

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.util.AbstractHBaseTool
      • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.util.LoadTestTool
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configurable, org.apache.hadoop.util.Tool

    @InterfaceAudience.LimitedPrivate(value="Tools")
public class LoadTestTool
extends org.apache.hadoop.hbase.util.AbstractHBaseTool
    A command-line utility that reads, writes, and verifies data. Unlike PerformanceEvaluation, this tool validates the data written, and supports simultaneously writing and reading the same set of keys.

      • parallelLoadTables

        private int parallelLoadTables()
                        throws IOException
        When NUM_TABLES is specified, the function starts multiple worker threads which individually start a LoadTestTool instance to load a table. Each table name is in format <tn>_<index>. For example, "-tn test -num_tables 2" , table names will be "test_1", "test_2"
        抛出:
        IOException - if one of the load tasks is unable to complete

                     throws IOException
